You shouldn't push it.

30
00:06:47,783 --> 00:06:49,648
I guess so. Sorry.

31
00:06:50,453 --> 00:06:52,421
I hope you recover soon.

32
00:06:52,521 --> 00:06:55,684
You look so happy
when you're playing.

33
00:06:56,058 --> 00:06:58,618
It's the one thing I do really well.

34
00:06:59,061 --> 00:07:01,325
Hey, why don't you try playing?

35
00:07:01,697 --> 00:07:05,531
