40
00:07:18,981 --> 00:07:21,176
Come over here, Yuna.

41
00:07:21,384 --> 00:07:22,146
Sure.

42
00:07:29,025 --> 00:07:30,959
This should do it.

43
00:07:32,294 --> 00:07:34,421
Now, sit in front of the piano.

44
00:07:34,764 --> 00:07:35,662
All right.

45
00:07:47,810 --> 00:07:49,539
That's amazing!

46
00:07:49,645 --> 00:07:52,546
Wow! It's perfect,
with no mistakes!

47
00:07:53,416 --> 00:07:55,509
Really? I'm glad.

48
00:07:56,052 --> 00:07:58,714
All right. I'm going
to teach you piano.

49
00:07:58,821 --> 00:08:01,654
I'm sure you'll be able
to play like a pro.

50
00:08:01,757 --> 00:08:03,657
If you're going to teach me...

51
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:05,488
I'll be sure to do my best.

52
00:08:05,594 --> 00:08:07,994
You're really cute.

53
00:08:46,402 --> 00:08:47,699
Oh, Seiji!

54
00:08:49,638 --> 00:08:51,697
This feels really good.

55
