61
00:10:18,561 --> 00:10:19,926
How was I?

62
00:10:20,262 --> 00:10:22,526
Needs a little more nuance.

63
00:10:26,502 --> 00:10:29,801
All right, I'm taking you
to a real concert...

64
00:10:29,905 --> 00:10:33,466
...since I can't play well enough
for you to be inspired.

65
00:10:33,976 --> 00:10:35,443
A concert?

66
00:10:36,045 --> 00:10:38,673
I've never been to a concert.

67
00:10:38,781 --> 00:10:42,444
Get ready then. I'll book
the tickets on-line.

68
00:10:43,352 --> 00:10:44,376
All right!

69
00:11:31,433 --> 00:11:32,593
What did you think?

70
00:11:33,502 --> 00:11:36,665
It was a great learning experience.

71
00:11:36,772 --> 00:11:38,569
Good. I have high hopes for you.

72
00:11:45,881 --> 00:11:48,179
Takeo, maybe we should
just go home.

73
00:11:48,851 --> 00:11:51,843
How dare a machine like
you tell me what to do!?

74
00:11:53,622 --> 00:11:56,921
Just shut up and follow me!

75
00:12:02,364 --> 00:12:04,889
I can have you replaced
just like that.

76
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:08,026
You talk back to me and
I'll have you taken away!

77
00:12:08,604 --> 00:12:11,471
Yes. I'm sorry, master.

78
00:12:11,573 --> 00:12:12,562
I'll never--

79
00:12:12,942 --> 00:12:16,469
Just shut up and come!
Let's get a drink!

80
00:12:20,282 --> 00:12:21,408
I'm scared.

81
00:12:22,184 --> 00:12:25,847
People who treat robots
like animals are scum.

82
00:12:29,058 --> 00:12:32,289
Seiji treats me really well.

83
00:12:33,028 --> 00:12:34,325
Like a human.

84
00:12:42,037 --> 00:12:43,334
What's wrong?

85
00:12:43,939 --> 00:12:46,407
A little shaken after
going out tonight?

86
00:12:46,575 --> 00:12:50,944
Well, no... You are a kind man,
aren't you?

87
