What do you mean?

88
00:12:53,248 --> 00:12:55,079
Thank you.

89
00:12:55,184 --> 00:12:59,484
I don't think of you as less
than human. That's all.

90
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:12,631
Seiji...

91
00:13:28,851 --> 00:13:30,648
It feels so good.

92
00:13:43,999 --> 00:13:45,227
Seiji...

93
00:13:59,348 --> 00:14:01,509
Yes... Yes...!

94
00:15:24,900 --> 00:15:27,767
Well, you've gotten much better.

95
00:15:27,870 --> 00:15:29,337
Thanks to you.

96
00:15:30,272 --> 00:15:32,137
We can do it if you're this good.

97
00:15:32,241 --> 00:15:34,436
Right. I'm going to arrange
your professional debut.

98
00:15:43,552 --> 00:15:47,113
Go get ready.
Let's go there directly.

99
00:15:47,222 --> 00:15:48,189
