142
00:18:53,709 --> 00:18:55,336
Is this the warranty company?

143
00:18:55,444 --> 00:18:57,935
My robot has gone missing.

144
00:18:58,046 --> 00:18:59,673
Please find her right away.

145
00:19:00,082 --> 00:19:03,518
Yes. She's a model DX-V999.

146
00:19:03,618 --> 00:19:06,416
