159
00:20:59,434 --> 00:21:02,130
See, you can do it if you try.

160
00:21:26,795 --> 00:21:28,160
Stop!

161
00:21:40,342 --> 00:21:41,240
Yuna.

162
00:22:10,205 --> 00:22:11,968
This music...

163
00:22:33,628 --> 00:22:34,890
Seiji.

164
00:22:46,141 --> 00:22:48,507
