173
00:23:17,138 --> 00:23:18,628
But...

174
00:23:18,740 --> 00:23:22,574
You seemed so happy
teaching me how to play.

175
00:23:26,014 --> 00:23:29,575
But you mustn't live
your dreams through me.

176
00:23:30,685 --> 00:23:32,346
