178
00:23:34,556 --> 00:23:36,888
That you will play again...

179
00:23:36,992 --> 00:23:38,550
...and return to the concert stage.

180
00:23:39,661 --> 00:23:40,559
Yuna.

181
00:23:40,862 --> 00:23:42,830
Seiji.

